import { Toolbar, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <React.Fragment>
      <Appbar>
        <Toolbar>
        <Typography>
          Logo
        </Typography>
        </Toolbar>
      </Appbar>
    </React.Fragment>
  )
}

export default Navbar
